EXT. CLIFFTOP — GOLDEN HOUR

Wide open sky. The sea far below.

CAMERA (shot 14) [lens=85mm, frame=WS]: Wide — SARAH against the horizon
LIGHT (setup 6) [type=natural, direction=left]: Sun as key — golden hour practical
SOUND (take 1) [boom=overhead, wind=reduce]: Boom from above, wind filter

SARAH stands at the edge, looking out.

